7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both CodeGPT and Pieces share a solid foundation of core features including Code Generation, Debugging, Multi Language, Ide Integration. Where CodeGPT pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Autocomplete, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. \n\nLooking at user ratings, CodeGPT holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Pieces scores 6/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
